{"tid":1176689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴國新娘嫁中國有錢人　婚後才知是鴨農　「連像樣的廁所都冇」","createTime":"2019-05-29T11:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:46:50.000Z","uid":66271,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb7c91fa2bfed989445bafee4d6e8a6411d7230","tid":1176689,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2850186/org/b12515e6ea2c177459fd4fb47f975d20.jpg/kdmIDd86FHznToOsunFIeuZFRA7ip3GSKmmBYippgWI?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2850186%2Forg%2Fb12515e6ea2c177459fd4fb47f975d20.jpg%2FkdmIDd86FHznToOsunFIeuZFRA7ip3GSKmmBYippgWI%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=308d1bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦伊斯蘭堡（Islamabad）22歲少女坎瓦爾（Rabia Kanwal）今年2月嫁給33歲中國山東男子張書臣，起初她以為嫁了個富有老公，從此離開貧民窟過好日子，然而婚後才知對方是個貧農，家中甚至連像樣的廁所也沒有，坎瓦爾憤而提出離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2850149/org/eec66eb30639df05335912e8c1b9b2e2.jpg/qOanyS8Zn7DVvnbT6XI6MX_qp41UtiRkFL7wkhS-8JI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2850149%2Forg%2Feec66eb30639df05335912e8c1b9b2e2.jpg%2FqOanyS8Zn7DVvnbT6XI6MX_qp41UtiRkFL7wkhS-8JI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ae41a105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坎瓦爾在貧民區長大，經介紹下認識了到當地旅遊的張書臣，當時他訛稱自己是一名「有錢的農場主人」。兩人雖然語言不通，但透過翻譯軟件溝通後，男方給坎瓦爾的父母留下不錯的印象，最終雙方決定談婚論嫁。坎瓦爾說：「我父母稱鄰居的女兒在中國很快樂，所以我也應會快樂」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2850153/org/8595456f24a0061efe4721d4c999b23f.jpg/vrDzgTB2NijN188yhC8kvcdctokvohkKv3crAr93KwI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2850153%2Forg%2F8595456f24a0061efe4721d4c999b23f.jpg%2FvrDzgTB2NijN188yhC8kvcdctokvohkKv3crAr93KwI&h=c818dd08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩人在巴基斯坦舉行婚禮，然後坎瓦爾隨丈夫回到中國山東省東張村，本來她對新婚生活滿懷希望，豈料夫家原來是務農的，而張書臣口中的「大規模農場」其實是一般農戶的養鴨場，而且住所偏僻簡陋，連一個像樣的廁所也沒有。更甚者，張書臣假裝是穆斯林，坎瓦爾說，張書臣向她背誦過穆斯林的第一信條，「但我從未見過他禮拜，連去到伊斯蘭堡著名的費薩爾清真寺（Faisal Mosque）時都沒有見過。」<br />\n<br />\n坎瓦爾表示，張書臣的家人曾將她反鎖在房中兩日，企圖逼她留下來，她於是想辦法聯絡巴基斯坦大使館，最後成功獲救回家，現正辦理離婚手續。她稱，待在中國的八天「很可怕，無法用語言形容」，而且「寧死也不願和他（張書臣）一起生活」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張書臣否認曾強逼坎瓦爾留下來，但承認當初給了婚姻介紹人1.45萬美元（約11.5萬港元）費用，並聽信對方建議，訛稱很有錢和信奉伊斯蘭教。他無奈地稱，如今婚姻告吹，只好繼續好好養鴨過日子。<br />\n<br />\n坎瓦爾已算很幸運，據報道，最近至少有150名巴基斯坦女子向當局投訴，聲稱被假婚姻騙到中國去，有的更被逼在酒吧和俱樂部等地方工作，甚至賣淫。人權觀察組織（Human Rights Watch）中國部主任理查森（Sophie Richardson）指出，越來越多的證據顯示，巴基斯坦女性有遭受性奴役的危險，巴基斯坦和中國都應該認真對待有關問題。"},{"pid":"bf2aabea5b3e5a142fde286dfd3047cacc1cdb04","tid":1176689,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14288396a298ba93eece2952b08981c798bff33f","tid":1176689,"uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f52ad4666ceeba6d713de537da4c19fabb73ad","tid":1176689,"uid":124584,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"有錢駛閪娶巴基咩 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵比人呃"},{"pid":"cb82d03cedb57c4023fc5a85d223aa9e2f971a17","tid":1176689,"uid":38518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c5066e2910efa873739802bb98509b766731c7","tid":1176689,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"成日J  arab  porn"},{"pid":"6bfa18c95ba6e75a41ecf855ea56cc26a1313285","tid":1176689,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c5066e2910efa873739802bb98509b766731c7","tid":1176689,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike"